          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/10192384-revelation-space">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/20498957-claudia?shelf=z-to-a-reynolds">z-to-a-reynolds</a>, 
