<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/51204.Alastair_Reynolds"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1521740247p3/51204.jpg);'></div>
